txt.en: 'Well done, friend! You sure put away those pies, and just in the nick of time!\n\n'As a winner of the pie-eating contest, you're welcome to claim your prize. Of course, you also have a wonderful title to go along with it: Pie-Eating Champion!'
The Pie-eating Contest
Time expired!
'Go on and eat! You're lagging behind!'
'Stuffed already? You've barely begun!'
Eat six pies within the allotted amount of time.
'Good, good...almost half-way done!'
Pies eaten (5/6)
Eat five more pies within the allotted amount of time.
'Oh dear, you look a bit flushed. Are you feeling ill?'
Eat pies (5/6)
Eat four more pies within the allotted amount of time.
'This is quite disturbing to watch, let me assure you!'
Pies eaten (6/6)
Eat three more pies within the allotted amount of time.
'You're almost done! Don't bother chewing, just finish it!'
Finish before time runs out!
Eat two more pies within the allotted amount of time.
'Good day to you as well!'
'Ah, you still have a bit of pie on your face there....'
Eat one more within the allotted amount of time.
'Well, well. If it isn't Bree's resident pie-eating champion!'
Stuffed and sticky with pie, you should now speak to the Pie-man.
'Come back for more, eh? Sorry...only one prize per contestant.'
Eat pies (0/6)
Pies eaten (1/6)
Eat pies (1/6)
Pies eaten (2/6)
Eat pies (2/6)
Pies eaten (3/6)
Eat pies (3/6)
Pies eaten (4/6)
Eat pies (4/6)
It is time for the pie-eating contest at the Bree-fields fair-ground. Come one, come all, and enjoy the fare.
'Look at the time, I really must be heading home for supper, and dinner!'

'Are you here for the pie-eating contest? Wonderful! I'll explain the rules...

'The goal is to eat any six of the pies there on the table. Big ones or small ones, it makes no difference to me! But be sure you let me know you are finished before the time expires.

'Are you ready to start?'
